nt social and political groups, that share common claims and adopt various forms of protest action. It is during the protest campaigns that a sense of community is created.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 04. Okt 2022) 0aBridgesxEnvironmental aspectsxItalyxMessina, Strait of. 0aBridgesxEnvironmental aspectszItalyzMessina, Strait of. 0aCommunitiesxItaly. 0aCommunitieszItaly. 0aEnvironmentalismxItaly. 0aEnvironmentalismzItaly. 0aHigh speed trainsxEnvironmental aspectsxItalyxSusa Valley. 0aHigh speed trainsxEnvironmental aspectszItalyzSusa Valley. 0aProtest movementsxItaly. 0aProtest movementszItaly. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / Political Process / General.2bisacsh1 aPiazza, Gianni, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978184545862140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781845458621423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781845458621/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK